Let's build a mini notification system using the Observer pattern, where users subscribe to specific groups (think channels or event categories) and get notified when something new happens in their group.

ðŸ§ª Scenario: Group-Based Notifications
- Subject: GroupTopic â€” like "Sports" or "Technology"
- Observers: UserSubscriber â€” users who want to receive updates
- Event: When a message is published to a group, notify all subscribers.


// Observer Interface
interface Subscriber {
    void receive(String topic, String message);
}

// Concrete Observer
class UserSubscriber implements Subscriber {
    private String name;

    public UserSubscriber(String name) {
        this.name = name;
    }

    @Override
    public void receive(String topic, String message) {
        System.out.println(name + " received update from " + topic + ": " + message);
    }
}

// Subject Interface
interface GroupTopic {
    void subscribe(Subscriber s);
    void unsubscribe(Subscriber s);
    void notifySubscribers(String message);
}

// Concrete Subject
class SportsTopic implements GroupTopic {
    private List<Subscriber> subscribers = new ArrayList<>();

    @Override
    public void subscribe(Subscriber s) {
        subscribers.add(s);
    }

    @Override
    public void unsubscribe(Subscriber s) {
        subscribers.remove(s);
    }

    @Override
    public void notifySubscribers(String message) {
        for (Subscriber s : subscribers) {
            s.receive("Sports", message);
        }
    }

    public void publish(String msg) {
        System.out.println("ðŸ“¢ Sports Update: " + msg);
        notifySubscribers(msg);
    }
}

// Demo Code
public class ObserverPatternNotificationDemo {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        SportsTopic sports = new SportsTopic();

        Subscriber kritika = new UserSubscriber("Kritika");
        Subscriber arjun = new UserSubscriber("Arjun");

        sports.subscribe(kritika);
        sports.subscribe(arjun);

        sports.publish("India won the test match!");
        sports.unsubscribe(arjun);
        sports.publish("New IPL schedule released.");
    }
}



ðŸ“¢ Sports Update: India won the test match!
Kritika received update from Sports: India won the test match!
Arjun received update from Sports: India won the test match!

ðŸ“¢ Sports Update: New IPL schedule released.
Kritika received update from Sports: New IPL schedule released.


